    dc:description "figure 5 Dimorphilus oophagus sp. nov.A:Adult female, dorsal view; cb:ciliary bands, e: eyespot, oo:intracelomic oocytes, pm:pharyngeal musculature, p: pygidium, tc: tuft of cilia.S1–S6 = segment 1–6 B: Juvenile female.C: Immunohistochemistry showing the prostomial ciliary arrangement of an adult female.Acb = anterior ciliary band, pcb = posterior ciliary band D: Immunohistochemistry showing the segmental ciliary bands of an adult female.E: Reconstruction of an adult female of Dimorphilus oophagus sp. nov.Scale bars: A= 100μm, B= 100μm, C= 50μm, D= 100μm." ;
